DataElement.preferredName: Biologically-Derived Material Product Material Effective Date and Time Range ISO21090.IVL.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A substance made from living organisms or things they produce. EXAMPLE(S): virus, therapeutic serum, toxin, antitoxin, vaccine, blood, blood component or derivative, allergenic product, analogous product The date and time span for when the material is active.
